{"tid":2025651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗都進化咗，鬥熱狗喎！","createTime":"2020-05-20T11:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:48:45.000Z","uid":41846,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a49a5b556bd303610c19ef342bf1064f0179cc63","tid":2025651,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwxW1Ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwxW1Ea.png&h=b19986b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吓，唔可以咁，大家都以泛民為敵人邊可以㗎？<br />\n政治大嬸判係熱狗嘅好朋友，絕對無<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">偽熱狗</span></strong></span>，<br />\n絕對唔可以分化，唔可以割席！<br />\n<br />\n應該要學白兵咁話：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不如我地放底黨派分歧， 不分彼此，一齊屌死泛民先啦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n熱狗與政治大嬸判之間卿卿我我！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0g4Kq59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0g4Kq59.png&h=f59c94c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p8NPCcO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp8NPCcO.png&h=de045988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGDbQzt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGDbQzt.png&h=c6c07f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yF8y3Uu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyF8y3Uu.png&h=b98930cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c5f56f916497500efdc6cad12b97cced7d702e","tid":202565